						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying in the Basavanakaṭṭa.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1587, <hi rend="bold">Viśvāvasu, Pushya śu. 15,</hi> corresponding to 1666 A.D., January 10, Wednesday.</p>						

						<p>It registers the exemptions of a certain <hi rend="italic">gutta</hi> on the village Pulivendula made by the chief Fateh Khan Sahit.</p>						

